    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a superlative example of the S54B32 platform. This high-strung 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, mechanical shift gates, feeding power through a reinforced subframe to the M-Variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear floor has been structurally reinforced to eliminate the common chassis fatigue found in lesser examples. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers. Every body panel displays consistent paint depth, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or UV degradation. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for the purist collector.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
