    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a seamless power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Critical preventative measures have been completed, including rod bearing replacement and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with no bushing deflection, and the hydraulic steering rack remains leak-free and communicative. Finished in original paint with perfect shut lines and a pristine underside, this example represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a mechanically superlative icon.",
